1 AN ACT
2 To enact R.S. 26:914.1, relative to permits for vapor products and modified risk tobacco
3 products; to provide requirements for certain permitted manufacturers and dealers
4 of vapor products; to provide for limitations and requirements; to exempt certain
5 sales of vapor products to affiliated entities; to provide for certain exceptions; to
6 provide for an effective date for implementation and imposition of the reduced tax
7 on modified risk tobacco products; and to provide for related matters.
8 Be it enacted by the Legislature of Louisiana:
9 Section 1. R.S. 26:914.1 is hereby enacted to read as follows:
10 §914.1. Three-tier system for vapor products
11 A.(1) No Louisiana-permitted manufacturer of vapor products shall do any
12 of the following:
13 (a) Hold a retail dealer permit issued pursuant to this Chapter for the purpose
14 of selling vapor products to Louisiana consumers.
15 (b) Hold a wholesale dealer permit issued pursuant to this Chapter for the
16 purpose of selling vapor products to Louisiana consumers.
17 (c) Possess any direct or indirect financial interest in a Louisiana-permitted
18 wholesale dealer or retail dealer of vapor products.
19 (2) No Louisiana-permitted wholesale dealer of vapor products shall hold a
20 retail dealer permit issued pursuant to this Chapter for the purpose of selling vapor
21 products to Louisiana consumers.
